SDASM.ADDITIONAL INFORMATION: Top row to Bottom: Vandehey, Tapp; Heil, Duerr, Beyl, Roseberry, Yellin, Sherren (KIA July 8, 1945), D.B. Moore, R.E. Moore, Brookes, Evans, Collins; Chambers, Carr (July 8, 1945), Hostether, Hollan, Gautsche, Maher. Taken the day before Major Van left for the states.
